          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Deck Themes"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "An eye‑catching theme will ensure your deck stands out from the crowd. Check out Dropdeck’s themes at any time from the Deck Sidebar."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "If you have a branded theme associated with your account, it will also be available here."
            }
